{{IPAfont|⟨imo<sub>1</sub>⟩}} → {{IPAchar|/imo/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=いも|-}}.

The medial {{IPAchar|/-m-/}} means "[[woman]], [[female]]", found in a number of related terms such as {{m|ja|女|tr=<i>me</i>, <i>onna</i>||[[woman]]}}, {{m|ja|嫗|tr=omina||[[elderly]] woman}}, and {{m|ja|母|tr=omo||[[mother]]|pos=archaic}}.

