# one's own [[younger]] [[sister]]
#: {{antonyms|ja|姉|tr=ane}}
# the [[wife]] of one's younger [[brother]]; one's [[sister-in-law]]
#: {{synonyms|ja|義妹|tr=gimai}}
# a younger [[female]]

